2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Joanna%20Newsom%20Announces%20Intimate%20Solo%20Concerts%20in%20Los%20Angeles%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710164971000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F03%2Fjoanna-newsom-the-orpheum-concert-review.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235938032%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Singer-songwriter-harpist%20and%20indie%20icon%20Joanna%20Newsom%2C%20who%20has%20kept%20a%20low%20profile%20since%20the%20tour%20supporting%20her%202015%20album%20%E2%80%9CDivers%2C%E2%80%9D%20has%20announced%20a%20five-night%20solo%20residency%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%20Billed%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9CStrings%2FKeys%20Incidence%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20shows%20will%20take%20place%20at%20the%20intimate%20Masonic%20Lodge%20at%20Hollywood%20Forever%20from%20May%2015-19.%20One%20of%20the%20shows%20is%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Jem%20Aswad%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fjoanna-newsom-solo-concerts-los-angeles-1235938032%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fjoanna-newsom-solo-concerts-los-angeles-1235938032%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fjoanna-newsom-solo-concerts-los-angeles-1235938032%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mission%20Divyastra%3A%20What%20Agni-5%20Missile%20With%20MIRV%20Tech%20Can%20Do%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20successfully%20conducted%20the%20first%20flight%20test%20of%20Multiple%20Independently%20Targetable%20Re-entry%20Vehicles%20(MIRV)%20with%20the%20Agni-5%20Intercontinental%20Ballistic%20Missile.%20The%20Defence%20Research%20and%20Development%20Organisation%20(DRDO)%20conducted%20a%20successful%20test%20of%20the%20MIRV%20technology%20which%20was%20in%20development%20for%20several%20years%2C%20putting%20India%20on%20an%20elite%20list%20of%20nations%20that%20have%20the%20capability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProud%20of%20DRDO%20scientists%20for%20Mission%20Divyastra%20the%20first%20flight%20test%20of%20indigenously%20developed%20Agni-5%20missile%20with%20Multiple%20Independently%20Targetable%20Re-entry%20Vehicle%20(MIRV)%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20announced%20on%20X.%20A%20woman%20DRDO%20scientist%20was%20the%20mission%20lead%20and%20several%20women%20scientists%20played%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20the%20mission%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20MIRV%20Technology%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScientists%20at%20DRDO%20have%20been%20working%20on%20the%20Multiple%20Independently%20Targetable%20Re-entry%20Vehicles%20(MIRV)%20technology%20for%20many%20years.%20The%20technology%20allows%20a%20single%20missile%20like%20the%20Agni-5%20to%20carry%20multiple%20warheads%20and%20target%20independently%20target%20multiple%20locations.%20The%20system%20developed%20by%20DRDO%20is%20equipped%20with%20indigenous%20Avionics%20systems%20and%20high-accuracy%20sensor%20packages%2C%20which%20ensured%20that%20the%20re-entry%20vehicles%20reached%20the%20target%20points%20within%20the%20desired%20accuracy%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F3bjebl4g_mirv-technology_625x300_11_March_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgni-5%20is%20an%20Intercontinental%20Ballistic%20Missile%20(ICBM)%20that%20goes%20into%20space%20before%20re-entering%20the%20atmosphere.%20With%20the%20MIRV%20technology%2C%20multiple%20targets%20located%20at%20different%20locations%20can%20be%20engaged%20from%20the%20same%20missile%20with%20several%20warheads.%20These%20warheads%20could%20be%20nuclear%20or%20non-nuclear.%20The%20technology%20allows%20a%20missile%20to%20carry%20several%20bombs.%20These%20bombs%20can%20target%20locations%20that%20can%20be%20several%20hundred%20kilometres%20apart.%20Some%20MIRVed%20missiles%20can%20even%20hit%20targets%20separated%20by%20a%20distance%20of%201%2C500%20kilometres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20capability%20allows%20states%20to%20engage%20multiple%20targets%20to%20have%20a%20first-strike%20move%20for%20an%20edge%20during%20times%20of%20war.%20Agni-5%20missile%20has%20been%20tested%20earlier%2C%20but%20only%20with%20a%20single%20warhead.%20A%20missile%2C%20when%20it%20re-enters%20the%20atmosphere%2C%20can%20reach%20up%20to%20at%20least%20five%20times%20the%20speed%20of%20sound%20(5%20Mach)%20with%20the%20help%20of%20Kinetic%20Energy%20as%20it%20loses%20altitude%20and%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20Anti-Missile%20Defence%20(AMD)%20systems%20is%20reduced%20with%20the%20MIRV%20technology%20as%20AMD%20is%20primarily%20deployed%20to%20engage%20single%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Agni-5%20missile%20has%20an%20operational%20range%20of%20at%20least%208%2C000%20km%20that%20can%20target%20cities%2C%20the%20MIRV%20technology%20puts%20multiple%20cities%20within%20that%20range%20under%20the%20target%2C%20providing%20a%20broader%20safety%20net%20and%20several%20locations%20under%20the%20missile's%20reach.%20The%20true%20range%20of%20missiles%20is%20always%20unknown.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20test%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-india-preps-for-missile-test-chinese-vessel-on-watch-off-vizag-coast-5218406%5C%22%3Ea%20NOTAM%20alert%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20issued%20last%20week.%20NOTAM%2C%20meaning%20notice%20to%20airmen%2C%20are%20alerts%20issued%20to%20designate%20an%20area%20as%20a%20no-fly%20zone.%20The%20alert%20was%20for%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20area%2C%20which%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20clear%20indication%20India%20is%20planning%20a%20missile%20test%20that%20may%20take%20place%20anytime%20between%20March%2011%20and%2016.%20This%20no-fly%20zone%20earmarked%20in%20the%20NOTAM%20alert%20spans%203%2C500%20kilometres%2C%20well%20into%20the%20south%20of%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20technology%20was%20originally%20developed%20in%20the%201960s%20and%20the%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20Russia%2C%20France%20and%20China%20can%20use%20it.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20Russian%20MIRVed%20missile%20under%20development%20may%20be%20able%20to%20carry%20up%20to%2016%20warheads%2C%20each%20in%20a%20separate%20re-entry%20vehicle.%20There%20are%20reports%20that%20Israel%20is%20also%20working%20on%20developing%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20technology%20requires%20a%20combination%20of%20large%20missiles%2C%20small%20warheads%2C%20accurate%20guidance%2C%20and%20a%20complex%20mechanism%20for%20releasing%20warheads%20sequentially%20during%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20was%20the%20first%20country%20to%20develop%20MIRV%20technology%2C%20deploying%20a%20MIRVed%20Intercontinental%20Ballistic%20Missile%20(ICBM)%20in%201970%20and%20a%20MIRVed%20Submarine-Launched%20Ballistic%20Missile%20(SLBM)%20in%201971.%20The%20Soviet%20Union%20quickly%20followed%20suit%20and%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%201970s%20had%20developed%20their%20MIRV-enabled%20ICBM%20and%20SLBM%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710164880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-03%2F8te4qn3g_missile-generic_625x300_27_March_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fall-about-mission-divyastra-single-missile-can-deploy-multiple-warheads-5218773%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20successfully%20conducted%20the%20first%20flight%20test%20of%20Multiple%20Independently%20Targetable%20Re-entry%20Vehicles%20(MIRV)%20with%20the%20Agni-5%20Intercontinental%20Ballistic%20Missile.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fall-about-mission-divyastra-single-missile-can