D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElon%20Musk.%3Cp%3ELEON%20NEAL%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EElon%20Musk's%20charity%20often%20supports%20his%20own%20interests%2C%20according%20to%20a%20New%20York%20Times%20analysis.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHalf%20of%20donations%20made%20in%202021%20and%202022%C2%A0had%20links%20to%20Musk%2C%20his%20employees%2C%20or%20his%20businesses%2C%20it%20found.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Musk%20Foundation%20also%20regularly%20falls%20short%20of%20minimum%20required%20donations%20set%20by%20tax%20laws%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk's%20charity%20makes%20infrequent%20donations%20and%20the%20ones%20it%20does%20make%20often%20support%20his%20own%20interests%2C%20according%20to%20an%20in-depth%20analysis%20by%20The%20New%20York%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20half%20of%20the%20donations%20made%20by%20Musk's%20charitable%20Musk%20Foundation%20in%202021%20and%202022%20had%20some%20link%20to%20him%2C%20one%20of%20his%20employees%2C%20or%20one%20of%20his%20businesses%2C%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F03%2F10%2Fus%2Felon-musk-charity.html%3Fsmid%3Dnytcore-ios-share%26referringSource%3DarticleShare%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20analysis%3C%2Fa%3E%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20in%20March%202021%20the%20Musk%20Foundation%20gave%20millions%20to%20Cameron%20County%20%E2%80%94%20a%20pledge%20made%20by%20Musk%20within%20hours%20of%20a%20SpaceX%20rocket%20blowing%20up%20and%20scattering%20metal%20across%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20donations%20included%20%2455%20million%20to%20help%20a%20major%20SpaceX%20customer%20meet%20a%20charitable%20pledge%20and%20donations%20to%20two%20schools%20closely%20tied%20to%20Musk's%20businesses%2C%20the%20paper%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%2C%20who%20owns%20Tesla%20and%20SpaceX%2C%20is%20the%20second-richest%20person%20in%20the%20world%20according%20to%20Forbes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%202020%2C%20he%20has%20seeded%20his%20charity%20with%20tax-deductible%20donations%20of%20stock%20worth%20billions%E2%80%94%20a%20way%20to%20reduce%20his%20own%20tax%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETax%20laws%20allow%20executives%20holding%20significant%20amounts%20of%20their%20company's%20stock%20to%20reduce%20their%20tax%20liability%20through%20charitable%20donations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%202021%2C%20Musk%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1472754632325795843%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erevealed%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20would%20have%20to%20pay%20over%20%2411%20billion%20in%20taxes%20after%20he%20exercised%20options%20from%20a%20stock%20bonus%20plan%20from%20Tesla%20that%20gave%20him%20about%20%2425%20billion%20worth%20of%20shares%20in%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20tax%20law%2C%20all%20foundations%20must%20give%20away%205%25%20of%20their%20assets%20every%20year.%20However%2C%20the%20Musk%20Foundation%20has%20failed%20in%20recent%20years%20to%20give%20away%20the%20minimum%20required%2C%20the%20Times%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20the%20Musk%20Foundation%20fell%20%2441%20million%20short%20of%20the%20minimum%20required%20donation%2C%20and%20in%202022%20it%20missed%20the%205%25%20required%20donation%20by%20%24193%20million%2C%20tax%20filings%20show%2C%20per%20the%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Musk%20Foundation%20has%20not%20reported%20what%20it%20gave%20away%20in%202023.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Times%2C%20if%20it%20did%20not%20address%20the%20shortfall%20from%20the%20previous%20year%2C%20it%20could%20incur%20a%20penalty%20tax%20amounting%20to%2030%25%20of%20the%20remaining%20shortfall%20from%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20contrasted%20Musk's%20philanthropic%20activities%20with%20fellow%20billionaire%20Bill%20Gates%2C%20whose%20charitable%20foundation%20is%20the%20second%20largest%20in%20the%20world%20and%20has%20had%20major%20global%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20r