EAnd%20it%20comes%20less%20than%20a%20month%20after%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20stressed%20the%20CAA%20will%20%26quot%3Bdefinitely%20be%20notified%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BCAA%20is%20an%20act%20of%20the%20country...%20it%20will%20definitely%20be%20notified.%20CAA%20will%20come%20into%20effect%20before%20the%20election%20(and)%20nobody%20should%20be%20confused%20about%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20also%20sought%20to%20play%20down%20fears%20the%20CAA%2C%20and%20the%20equally%20contentious%20NRC%2C%20or%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%2C%20will%20be%20combined%20to%20target%20religious%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20who%20has%20long%20been%20one%20of%20the%20CAA's%20fiercest%20and%20most%20vocal%20critics%2C%20has%20hit%20out%20almost%20immediately%2C%20telling%20reporters%20at%20a%20hastily-convened%20presser%20that%20her%20government%20will%20oppose%20%26quot%3Banything%20that%20discriminates%20(against)%20people%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20boss%20also%20pointed%20out%20the%20CAA%2C%20the%20NRC%2C%20and%20the%20NPR%2C%20or%20National%20Population%20Register%2C%20were%20sensitive%20topics%20in%20Bengal%20and%20the%20northeast%20-%20in%20parts%20of%20which%20the%20CAA%20has%20been%20exempted%20by%20the%20centre%20-%20and%20that%20she%20does%20not%20want%20unrest%20before%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20she%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20raking%20up%20the%20CAA%20issue%20at%20this%20time%20for%20votes.%20%26quot%3BWith%20elections%20approaching%2C%20BJP%20has%20again%20raked%20up%20CAA%20issue%20to%20reap%20political%20benefits.%20But%20let%20me%20make%20it%20clear%2C%20as%20long%20as%20I%20am%20alive%2C%20I%20will%20not%20allow%20it%20in%20Bengal%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20northeast%20-%20which%20saw%20violent%20clashes%20between%20anti-CAA%20protesters%20and%20the%20police%2C%20the%20Assam%20Students%20Union%2C%20which%20led%20protests%20in%20the%20state%20four%20years%20ago%2C%20has%20sounded%20the%20call%20for%20another%20agitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20isn't%20the%20only%20opposition%20politician%20to%20fight%20against%20the%20CAA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee's%20Tamil%20Nadu%20counterpart%2C%20MK%20Stalin%2C%20was%20similarly%20emphatic.%20Accusing%20the%20BJP%20government%20of%20going%20%26quot%3Bagainst%20communal%20harmony%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20DMK%20boss%20too%20vowed%20he%20would%20not%20implement%20the%20law.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20states%20-%20like%20Kerala%20and%20Punjab%20-%20and%20others%20then%20ruled%20by%20the%20Congress%20(and%20now%20by%20the%20BJP)%20-%20such%20as%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20-%20also%20opposed%20the%20CAA%20and%20passed%20resolutions.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20Bengal%20and%20Kerala%20governments%20also%20stopped%20all%20NPR%2C%20or%20National%20Population%20Register%2C%20and%20NRC%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Telangana%2C%20the%20then-ruling%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20of%20ex-Chief%20Minister%20K%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%20also%20passed%20resolutions%20against%20all%20three%20and%20urged%20the%20government%20to%20%26quot%3Bremove%20all%20references%20to%20any%20religion%2C%20or%20to%20any%20foreign%20country%26quot%3B%20in%20view%20of%20fears%20expressed%20by%20lakhs%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20government%20-%20then%20also%20ruled%20by%20the%20Congress%20-%20also%20passed%20a%20resolution%2C%20and%2C%20significantly%2C%20several%20BJP%20leaders%20and%20lawmakers%20from%20the%20state%20also%20criticised%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20said%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20will%20help%20minorities%20from%20Muslim-dominated%20countries%20get%20citizenship%20if%20they%20fled%20due%20to%20religious%20persecution.%20However%2C%20critics%20say%20it%20is%20designed%20to%20discriminate%20against%20Muslims%20and%20violat