in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2F07121932%2FUntitled-design-2021-12-07T121919.360.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Union%20home%20affairs%20ministry%20will%20notify%20the%20rules%20to%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20(CAA)%2C%202019%20on%20Monday%20(March%2011)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPIBHomeAffairs%2Fstatus%2F1767173421727711374%5C%22%3Eit%20said%20in%20a%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20applications%20will%20be%20submitted%20in%20a%20completely%20online%20mode%20for%20which%20a%20web%20portal%20has%20been%20provided%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20continued%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAA%20aims%20to%20provide%20citizenship%20to%20Hindus%2C%20Parsis%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20Buddhists%2C%20Jains%20and%20Christians%20purportedly%20fleeing%20persecution%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20Muslim-majority%20neighbours%20%E2%80%93%20namely%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20Afghanistan%20and%20Bangladesh%20%E2%80%93%20and%20who%20arrived%20in%20India%20before%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20without%20rules%20being%20framed%2C%20the%20Act%20could%20not%20be%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exclusion%20of%20Muslims%20from%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20legislation%20and%20fears%20that%20it%20would%20disenfranchise%20many%20Muslims%20in%20India%20when%20combined%20with%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%20had%20drawn%20widespread%20protests%20from%20thousands%20of%20citizens%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20protests%20and%20violence%20that%20ensued%2C%20the%20government%20notified%20the%20law%20in%20January%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHome%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20last%20month%20that%20the%20rules%20for%20the%20CAA%20would%20be%20notified%20before%20the%20general%20elections%2C%20which%20are%20expected%20to%20take%20place%20between%20April%20and%20May%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoments%20after%20the%20home%20affairs%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20statement%20on%20X%2C%20the%20BJP%20also%20issued%20a%20statement%20on%20the%20social%20media%20platform%2C%20calling%20the%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20decision%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwatershed%20moment%20in%20the%20history%20of%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EA%20watershed%20moment%20in%20the%20history%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeartfelt%20thanks%20for%20making%20CAA%20a%20reality!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FT36zZRLeAs%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FT36zZRLeAs%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20BJP%20(%40BJP4India)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBJP4India%2Fstatus%2F1767175927358959837%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2011%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20parties%20however%2C%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20BJP%20government%20for%20notifying%20the%20rules%20just%20weeks%20ahead%20of%20the%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Kolkata%20before%20the%20home%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20announcement%2C%20West%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20said%20that%20the%20her%20Trinamool%20Congress%20party%2C%20which%20has%20opposed%20the%20CAA%20in%20the%20past%2C%20will%20first%20study%20its%20rules%20to%20see%20if%20it%20is%20depriving%20people%20of%20their%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLet%20me%20see%20the%20rules%20first.%20I%20am%20just%20watching.%20The%20notification%20and%20rules%20are%20not%20out%20yet.%20Once%20they%20are%20out%2C%20we%20will%20see%20if%20%5Bpeople%5D%20%E2%80%A6%20are%20being%20deprived%20of%20their%20rights%20under%20the%20rules%2C%20then%20we%20will%20fight%20against%20it.%20Let%20us%20study%20it%20properly%20first%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBanerjee%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CBut%20this%20is%20the%20BJP%E2