0education%20institutions%20are%20being%20starved%20of%20funds%2C%20setting%20the%20ground%20for%20privatisation%20and%20corporatisation%20of%20our%20universities%3B%20a%20steady%20deterioration%20of%20law%20and%20order%2C%20with%20instances%20of%20mob%20lynchings%2C%20rapes%2C%20organised%20crime%2C%20looting%2C%20drug%20trafficking%20all%20on%20the%20rise%20and%20being%20committed%20with%20impunity%3B%20sectarian%20violence%20has%20killed%20hundreds%2C%20women%20have%20been%20raped%20and%20paraded%20naked%20in%20Manipur%3B%20Muslims%20are%20attacked%2C%20as%20are%20Dalits%2C%20Adivasis%20and%20increasingly%20the%20Christians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMay%20we%2C%20the%20women%20of%20India%2C%20unite%20to%20voice%20our%20vigorous%20dissent%20of%20the%20anti-poor%2C%20anti-women%2C%20anti-minorities%20policies%20of%20the%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20declaration%20read%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20at%20Kittur%20Fort%2C%20let%20us%20pledge%20to%20use%20the%20power%20vested%20in%20us%20to%20defeat%20this%20patriarchal%2C%20autocratic%20and%20fascist%20regime%2C%20to%20bring%20about%20change%2C%20to%20vote%20out%20this%20government%20at%20the%20Centre!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20activist%20Anjali%20Bhardwaj%2C%20legal%20consultant%20Leena%20Dabiru%2C%20historian%20Mridula%20Mukherjee%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights%20activist%20and%20educationist%20Dr%20Syeda%20Hameed%20and%20Hashmi%20participated%20in%20the%20Delhi%20event%2C%20as%20per%20the%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710162009000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11175513%2FScreen-Shot-2024-03-11-at-5.54.32-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fkittur-declaration-a-call-for-women-in-india-to-resist-anti-women-anti-poor-anti-democratic-forces%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20declaration%20underlined%20various%20issues%20like%20leading%20activists%2C%20academics%20and%20journalists%20are%20behind%20bars%20without%20access%20to%20the%20legal%20provision%20of%20bail%3B%20higher%20education%20institutions%20are%20being%20starved%20of%20funds.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fkittur-declaration-a-call-for-women-in-india-to-resist-anti-women-anti-poor-anti-democratic-forces%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Airbnb%20bans%20security%20cameras%20indoors%20worldwide%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223485%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20phone%20showing%20the%20Airbnb%20app%20on%20the%20app%20store%2C%20with%20the%20Airbnb%20logo%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650b07e112dc4f001a173fe0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222319%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAirbnb%20is%20banning%20indoor%20security%20cameras%20after%20consulting%20with%20hosts%2C%20guests%2C%20and%20privacy%20experts.%20%3Cp%3EPhoto%20by%20Lorenzo%20Di%20Cola%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EStarting%20April%2030%2C%20Airbnb%20will%20ban%20any%20indoor%20security%20camera%20that%20could%20capture%20guest%20activities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECameras%20were%20previously%20allowed%20if%20they%20were%20disclosed%20in%20the%20online%20listing%20description.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHosts%20have%20said%20cameras%20protect%20property%2C%20while%20some%20guests%20have%20worried%20about%20being%20spied%20on.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAirbnb%20is%20officially%20banning%20the%20use%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-security-camera-home%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esecurity%20cameras%3C%2Fa%3E%20inside%20its%20listings%2C%20the%20short-term%20rental%20giant%20said%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHosts%20have%20until%20April%2030%20to%20remove%20any%20cameras%20from%20hallways%2C%20common%20rooms%2C%20and%20other%20interior%20spaces%20where%20they%20were%20previously%20permitted.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUntil%20now%2C%20cameras%20were%20allowed%20inside%20Airbnbs%20if%20hosts%20disclosed%20their%20presence%20in%20their%20online%20listings%2C%20warning%20guests%20ahead%20of%20time.%20Now%20Airbnb%20said%20it%20is%20changing%20its%20policy%20to%20a%20blanket%20ban%20after%20consulting%20with%20%26quot%3Bguests%2C%20hosts%2C%20and%20privacy%20experts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-outdoor-security-cameras%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOutdoor%20security%20cameras%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20remain%20in%20place%2C%20as%20long%20as%20they%20are%20disclosed%20in%20the%20listings.%20Doorbell%20cameras%20and%20noise%20monitors%20will%20still%20be%20allowed.%20Cameras%20in%20sleeping%20areas%20were%20previously%20banned%20by%20Airbnb.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20April%2030%2C%20reported%20violations%20of%20the%20policy%20could%20result%20in%20the%20removal%20of%20a%20host's%20listing%20or%20their%20entire%20account%2C%20according%20to%20a%20statement%20from%20Airbnb%20on%20the%20security%20camera%20ban.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAirbnb%20security%20cameras%20divide%20hosts%20and%20guests%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHosts%20and%20guests%20have%20clashed%20in%20the%20past%20on%20the%20use%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairbnb-short-term-rental-security-cameras-controversy-hosts-privacy-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esecurity%20cameras%20in%20Airbnbs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20hosts%20have%20maintained%20that%20cameras%20are%20integral%20to%20the%20upkeep%20of%20their%20short-term%20rentals%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20hold%20guests%20accountable%20for%20damage%20or%20prevent%20parties%20from%20being%20thrown.%20(Parties%20are%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairbnb-makes-party-ban-permanent-policy-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebanned%20by%20Airbnb%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArizona%20host%20Zach%20Narus%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%202023%20that%20cameras%20afforded%20him%20%26quot%3Bpeace%20of%20mind%26quot%3B%20during%20guest%20stays.%20Narus%20believed%20the%20cameras%20kept%20guests%20%26quot%3Bhonest%26quot%3B%20and%20also%20allowed%20him%20to%20troubleshoot%20issues%20that%20might%20arise%20as%20he%20managed%20a%20two-bedroom%20cabin%20remotely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELisa%20Lewis%20said%20last%20year%20that%20cameras%20were%20essential%20to%20running%20her%20two-bedroom%20rental%20in%20Foley%2C%20Alabama%2C%20a%20city%20near%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico's%20beaches%20and%20the%20Florida%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20used%20the%20footage%20to%20make%20sure%20guests%20were%20not%20unaccompanied%20minors%20and%20that%20they%20were%20not%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairbnb-uses-ai-to-identify-guests-hosting-house-parties-booking-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehosting%20large%20get-togethers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Lewis%20said%20she%20also%20used%20the%20camera%20to%20charge%20%24100%20to%20guests%20who%20attempted%20to%20check%20in%20early%20or%20check%20out%20late%20without%20first%20informing%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20guests%2C%20however%2C%20have%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20feeling%20watched.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20person%20posted%20on%20Twitter%20in%202021%20that%20they%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fvirtualkayluh%2Fstatus%2F1454331515442118657%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewere%20spied%20on%20while%20using%20the%20pool%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20an%20Airbnb%20after%2011%20p.m.%20In%202019%2C%20Florida%20resident%20Max%20Vest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theatlantic.com%2Ftechnology%2Farchive%2F2019%2F03%2Fwhat-happens-when-you-find-cameras-your-airbnb%2F585007%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20The%20Atlantic%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he