te%2C%20it%20will%20need%20about%2045%25%20vote%20share%20to%20hit%20Modi's%20target.%20No%20party%20can%20match%20the%20well-oiled%2C%20tech-savvy%2C%20cash-rich%20BJP%20organisation%20and%20its%20grassroots%20reach%20backed%20by%20the%20disciplined%20cadre%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20down%20to%20the%20booth%20level.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Modi%20is%20able%20to%20manifest%20the%20kind%20of%20victory%20he%20is%20aiming%20for%2C%20the%20country%20will%20cross%20the%20rubicon%20to%20a%20level%20of%20one-party%20dominance%20that%20will%20be%20difficult%20to%20reverse.%20Foreign%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%20assured%20a%20Japanese%20audience%20last%20week%20that%20India%20will%20have%20a%20stable%20government%20with%20a%20parliamentary%20majority%20for%20at%20least%20the%20next%2015%20years%2C%20if%20not%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EModi%20And%20The%20Ram%20Temple%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ever-on-the-move%20election%20juggernaut%20of%20the%20BJP%20shifted%20gears%20on%20the%20day%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20was%20consecrated%2C%20reminding%20Hindu%20voters%20of%20a%20pledge%20redeemed%20and%20Kashi%20and%20Mathura%20as%20promises%20in%20progress.%20The%20ceremony%20was%20also%20akin%20to%20a%20coronation%2C%20with%20the%20focus%20unwaveringly%20on%20PM%20Modi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20he%20led%20the%20ceremonies%2C%20one%20of%20the%20speakers%20compared%20him%20to%20Shivaji%2C%20the%20Maratha%20king%2C%20subtly%20signalling%20that%20a%20person%20who%20was%20not%20born%20in%20an%20upper%20caste%20was%20leading%20a%20Hindu%20religious%20ceremony%2C%20and%2C%20by%20extension%2C%20a%20new%20nation%20that%20was%20not%20the%20inheritance%20of%20the%20high-born.%20The%20protest%20from%20the%20Shankaracharyas%20reinforced%20the%20theme%2C%20reminding%20even%20more%20of%20Shivaji's%2017th-century%20coronation%2C%20for%20which%20he%20had%20to%20get%20priests%20from%20Varanasi%20at%20a%20great%20cost%20given%20that%20no%20local%20Brahmins%20would%20place%20the%20crown%20on%20his%20head%20as%20they%20believed%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Blow-born%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EConfident%20Yet%20Cautious%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20Modi's%20popularity%2C%20the%20BJP's%20election%20campaign%20rests%20on%20a%20two-pronged%20strategy%3A%20a%20strong%20Hindu%20nation%20rubbing%20shoulders%20with%20world%20powers%2C%20and%20an%20economic%20powerhouse%20that%20will%20set%20millions%20of%20citizens%20on%20the%20road%20to%20riches.%20While%20one%20half%20of%20the%20strategy%20is%20fairly%20successful%2C%20it%20is%20the%20second%20part%20where%20voters'%20minds%20are%20unclear.%20As%20the%20Pakistan%20elections%20proved%20recently%2C%20irrespective%20of%20the%20hurdles%20placed%20in%20their%20path%2C%20voters%20are%20capable%20of%20surprises.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20is%20more%20acutely%20conscious%20of%20this%20than%20the%20BJP.%20Also%20because%20it%20is%20haunted%20by%20its%20own%20defeat%20in%202004%20when%20it%20missed%20the%20woods%20for%20the%20trees.%20Blinded%20by%20booming%20stock%20markets%20and%20soaring%20corporate%20profits%2C%20its%20leaders%20failed%20to%20see%20the%20economic%20distress%20at%20the%20grassroots.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20economic%20situation%20would%20have%20resembled%20that%20of%202004%20if%20not%20for%20free%20food%2C%20some%20free%20cash%20and%20an%20ever-expanding%20rural%20jobs%20programme%2C%20which%20was%20once%20pilloried%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20himself%20as%20merely%20digging%20pits.%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Odisha%2C%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20saw%20demand%20for%20work%20under%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act%20(MNREGA)%20rising%20sharply%20in%202023.%20Although%20the%20farmers'%20strike%20in%20Delhi%20gives%20the%20appearance%20of%20largely%20a%20Punjab%20phenomenon%2C%20unpredictable%20weather%20destroying%20crops%20and%20knee-jerk%20policy%20changes%2C%20such%20as%20export%20bans%20to%20curb%20inflation%20and%20keep%20the%20middle-class%20consumer%20happy%2C%20have%20affected%20agriculturists%20across%20the%20country.%20The%20worst%20affected%20are%20landless%20farm%20workers.%20The%20flow%20of%20workers%20from%20farms%20to%20factories%20reversed%20about%20four%20years%20ago%20and%20is%20now%20virtually%20an%20exodus.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOdds%20Are%20In%20BJP's%20Favour%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20belligerence%20and%20noise%20of%20the%20grassroot%20workers%20of%20the%20RSS%20and%20the%20BJP%20have%20made%20sure%20that%20ordinary%20people%20do%20not%20speak%20their%20minds%20in%20public.%20Critical%20voices%20even%20from%20within%20the%20organisations%20are%20being%20shouted%20down.%20With%20a%20decent%20opposition%20near%20absent%2C%20the%20odds%20are%20heavily%20stacked%20in%20the%20BJP's%20favour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20WhatsApp%20campaign%2C%20the%20BJP%20exhorts%20voters%20to%20keep%20their%20weapon-vote-ready%20as%20the%20war%20to%20protect%20democracy%20is%20hither.%20%26quot%3BSoldiers%20are%20guarding%20our%20nation%20at%20the%20borders.%20We%20have%20to%20fight%20the%20traitors%20within%20the%20country%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20BJP%20achieves%20Modi's%20target%2C%20the%20sentiment%20underpinning%20its%20victory%20would%20easily%20be%20interpreted%20as%20a%20vote%20for%20a%20muscular%20Hindu%20nation.%20But%20if%20it%20ends%20up%20closer%20or%20below%20its%20current%20seat%20count%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20hint%20that%20they%20value%20their%20economic%20future%20more%20than%20religious%20hegemony.%20That%20is%20why%20this%20is%20a%20decisive%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20writer%20is%20editor%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdaily.thesignal.co%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20Signal%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20author%20of%20The%20RSS%20And%20The%20Maki