0Elizabeth%2C%20a%20report%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20is%20the%20second%20time%20in%20recent%20weeks%20that%20the%20carrier%20has%20suffered%20a%20problem.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELast%20month%2C%20HMS%20Queen%20Elizabeth%20pulled%20out%20of%20a%20NATO%20exercise%20following%20a%20mechanical%20issue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UK's%20%243.7%20billion%20flagship%20aircraft%20carrier%20caught%20fire%20in%20yet%20another%20embarrassment%20for%20the%20Royal%20Navy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fire%20broke%20out%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fukdefencejournal.org.uk%2Fbritish-aircraft-carrier-catches-fire-no-fatalities%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHMS%20Queen%20Elizabeth%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhile%20it%20was%20docked%20for%20repairs%20at%20Glen%20Mallan%20on%20Loch%20Long%20in%20Scotland%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fukdefencejournal.org.uk%2Fbritish-aircraft-carrier-catches-fire-no-fatalities%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUK%20Defence%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20second%20incident%20for%20the%20carrier%20in%20recent%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fire%2C%20which%20a%20Royal%20Navy%20spokesperson%20told%20the%20publication%20was%20%26quot%3Bminor%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20swiftly%20contained%20without%20reported%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20person%20aboard%20the%20ship%20told%20the%20Journal%3A%20%26quot%3BNo%20fatalities%2C%20minor%20fire%20damage%20to%20the%20ship%20but%20all%20over%20with.%26quot%3B%20The%20Royal%20Navy%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.navylookout.com%2Farticles%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENavy%20Lookout%2C%20a%20navy%20analysis%20site%2C%20wrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%26quot%3Bminor%20shipboard%20fires%20are%20not%20uncommon.%20All%20sailors%20are%20trained%20in%20fire-fighting%20and%2C%20in%20this%20instance%2C%20appear%20to%20have%20responded%20quickly%20and%20extinguished%20fire%20with%20no%20injuries.%20Involvement%20of%20local%20civilian%20fire%20brigade%20is%20also%20standard%20procedure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHMS%20Queen%20Elizabeth%20is%20now%20en%20route%20to%20Rosyth%2C%20Scotland%2C%20for%20repairs%2C%20specifically%20targeting%20the%20starboard%20propeller%20shaft%20coupling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20carrier%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuks-flagship-carrier-embarrassing-setback-pulls-out-big-nato-exercise-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewithdrawn%20from%20a%20major%20NATO%20exercise%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20of%20the%20coupling%20issue%2C%20and%20was%20ultimately%20replaced%20by%20HMS%20Prince%20of%20Wales.%20The%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20told%20BI%20at%20the%20time%20that%20technical%20problems%20were%20inevitable%20on%20state-of-the-art%20ships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHMS%20Prince%20of%20Wales%20itself%20faced%20breakdowns%20previously%2C%20adding%20to%20a%20pattern%20of%20mechanical%20difficulties%20in%20the%20Navy's%20flagship%20vessels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPressure%20is%20now%20mounting%20on%20UK%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20to%20increase%20defense%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EForeign%20Office%20Minister%20Anne-Marie%20Trevelyan%20and%20Security%20Minister%20Tom%20Tugendhat%20are%20advocating%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bmuch%20greater%20pace%26quot%3B%20of%20investment%2C%20stressing%20the%20need%20for%20the%20UK%20to%20lead%20in%20defense%20and%20security%20spending%2C%20particularly%20in%20light%20of%20escalating%20global%20risks%20posed%20by%20countries%20like%20Russia%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20underfunding%20of%20the%20Navy%20amid%20geopolitical%20strife%2C%20including%20vessels%20targeted%20by%20Houthis%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%20has%20called%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuk-navy-ships-breaking-down-britain-struggling-hms-queen-elizabeth-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%