0Test%2C%20Chinese%20Vessel%20On%20Watch%20Off%20Vizag%20Coast%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWithin%20days%20of%20India%20issuing%20an%20alert%20for%20an%20impending%20missile%20test%20off%20the%20Odisha%20coast%2C%20a%20Chinese%20research%20vessel%20has%20raced%20up%20India's%20eastern%20seaboard%20and%20is%20currently%20anchored%20in%20international%20waters%20off%20the%20Indian%20coastline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20test%20-%20of%20the%20Agni-5%20missile%20which%20has%20Multiple%20Independently%20Targetable%20Re-entry%20Vehicle%20(MIRV)%20technology%20-%C2%A0took%20place%20successfully%20on%20Monday.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20confirmed%20the%20successful%20test%20with%20a%20post%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chinese%20ship%2C%20Xian%20Yang%20Hong%2001%2C%20is%20now%20less%20than%20260%20nautical%20miles%20-%20about%20480%20kilometres%20-%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Visakhapatnam.%20Incidentally%2C%20that's%20where%20India%20bases%20its%20three%20nuclear-powered%20ballistic%20missile%20submarines%2C%20arguably%20the%20most%20sensitive%20weapons%20systems%20in%20India's%20arsenal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20reports%20the%20missile%20India%20was%20planning%20was%20the%20K-4%2C%20a%20nuclear%20capable%20missile%20designed%20to%20be%20launched%20by%20submarines.%20The%20missile%20was%20designed%20by%20the%20Defence%20Research%20Development%20Organisation%20(DRDO)%20and%20is%20capable%20of%20carrying%20warheads%20weighing%20up%20to%202%20tonnes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20test%20a%20NOTAM%20alert%20was%20issued%20last%20week.%20NOTAM%2C%20meaning%20notice%20to%20airmen%2C%20are%20alerts%20issued%20to%20designate%20an%20area%20as%20a%20no-fly%20zone.%20The%20alert%20was%20for%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20area%2C%20which%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20clear%20indication%20India%20is%20planning%20a%20missile%20test%20that%20may%20take%20place%20anytime%20between%20March%2011%20and%2016.%20This%20no-fly%20zone%20earmarked%20in%20the%20NOTAM%20alert%20spans%203%2C500%20kilometres%2C%20well%20into%20the%20south%20of%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20been%20monitoring%20India's%20activities%2C%20including%20missile%20tests%20off%20the%20eastern%20seaboard.%20Hence%2C%20the%20positioning%20of%20Xiang%20Yang%20Hong%2001%2C%20a%204%2C813-tonne%20research%20vessel%2C%20and%20the%20timing%20has%20raised%20suspicion.%20NDTV%20has%20tracked%20how%20the%20ship%20has%20changed%20its%20position%20over%20the%20past%20week%20before%20reaching%20its%20current%20location.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20Inputs%3A%20Damien%20Symon%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22With%20Inputs%3A%20Damien%20Symon%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F5sp49tq8_map_625x300_11_March_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Inputs%3A%20Damien%20Symon%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20vessel%20entered%20the%20Malacca%20straits%20on%20March%206%20and%20was%20spotted%20between%20the%20Great%20Nicobar%20Island%20and%20Indian%20peninsula%20on%20March%208.%C2%A0The%20ship%2C%20which%20went%20into%20service%20in%202016%2C%20is%20about%20100%20metres%20long%20and%20has%20a%20range%20of%2015%2C000%20nautical%20miles%2C%20according%20to%20reports%20in%20the%20Chinese%20state%20media.%20It%20has%20remote%20sensing%20equipment%20that%20can%20enable%20exploration%20to%20depths%20up%20to%2010%2C000%20metres%2C%20the%20reports%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20believed%20that%20the%20ship%20has%20sensors%20to%20detect%20sub-surface%20acoustic%20signatures.%20This%20means%20it%20may%20sense%20sound%20associated%20with%20the%20of%20submarines.%20These%20sounds%20can%20be%20detected%20through%20the%20ship's%20sonar%20and%20the%20buoys%20it%20deploys%2C%20and%20this%20may%20be%20used%20to%20record%20the%20acoustic%20footprints%20of%20submarines%20and%20possible%20underwater%20launches.%20This%20information%20is%20nothing%20less%20than%20an%20inte