could%20issue%20a%20notification%20later%20tonight%20to%20implement%20the%20controversial%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20Monday%20afternoon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAA%20-%20which%20makes%20religion%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20a%20test%20of%20citizenship%20-%20was%20cleared%20by%20Parliament%20in%20December%202019%20amid%20violent%20protests%20across%20the%20country%2C%20and%20fierce%20resistance%20from%20opposition%20politicians%20and%20the%20chief%20ministers%20of%20non-BJP%20states.%20Over%20100%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20those%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20issued%2C%20the%20government%20can%20grant%20Indian%20nationality%20to%20non-Muslim%20migrants%20from%20Bangladesh%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20Afghanistan%2C%20who%20had%20come%20to%20India%20before%202015.%20An%20unnamed%20official%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%20%26quot%3Bthe%20regulations%20are%20prepared%20and%20an%20online%20portal%20is%20already%20set%20up...%20applicants%20can%20disclose%20year%20of%20entry%20without%20travel%20documents%26quot%3B.%20No%20additional%20documents%20will%20be%20required%2C%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20less%20than%20a%20month%20after%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20stressed%20the%20CAA%20will%20be%20implemented%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20which%20is%20due%20in%20April%2FMay.%20%26quot%3BCAA%20is%20an%20act%20of%20the%20country...%20it%20will%20definitely%20be%20notified.%20CAA%20will%20come%20into%20effect%20before%20the%20election%20(and)%20nobody%20should%20be%20confused%20about%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20last%20month%20sought%20to%20play%20down%20fears%20the%20CAA%2C%20and%20the%20equally%20contentious%20NRC%2C%20or%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%2C%20will%20be%20combined%20to%20target%20minority%20communities.%20%26quot%3BOur%20Muslim%20brothers%20are%20being%20misled%20and%20instigated.%20CAA%20is%20only%20meant%20to%20give%20citizenship%20to%20those%20who%20came%20to%20India%20after%20facing%20persecution%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20Afghanistan%20and%20Bangladesh.%20It%20is%20not%20for%20snatching%20anyone's%20citizenship.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssurances%20the%20CAA%20will%20be%20implemented%20has%20been%20a%20key%20election%20promise%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20both%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20and%20in%20campaigns%20for%20various%20state%20polls%2C%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20the%202021%20election%20in%20Bengal%2C%20in%20which%20the%20saffron%20party%20and%20the%20ruling%20Trinamool%20staged%20high-profile%20and%20volatile%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Bengal%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20had%20lashed%20out%20at%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20again%20-%20this%20time%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20-%20accusing%20her%20of%20misleading%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20now%2C%20as%20the%20CAA%20nears%20notification%20(and%20implementation)%2C%20opposition%20politicians%2C%20including%20Ms%20Banerjee%2C%20have%20spoken%20out%20again%2C%20insisting%20it%20will%20not%20be%20enforced%20in%20their%20respective%20territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20BJP%20-%20bidding%20for%20a%20third%20term%20at%20the%20centre%20-%20had%20only%20raised%20the%20issue%20now%20for%20votes.%20%26quot%3BWith%20elections%20approaching%2C%20BJP%20has%20again%20raked%20up%20CAA%20issue%20to%20reap%20political%20benefits.%20But%20let%20me%20make%20it%20clear%2C%20as%20long%20as%20I%20am%20alive%2C%20I%20will%20not%20allow%20it%20in%20Bengal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee's%20Tamil%20Nadu%20counterpart%2C%20MK%20Stalin%2C%20was%20similarly%20emphatic.%20Accusing%20the%20BJP%20government%20of%20going%20%26quot%3Bagainst%20communal%20harmony%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20DMK%20boss%20too%20vowed%20he%20would%20not%20implement%20the%20law.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20states%20-%20like%20Kerala%20and%20Punjab%20-%20and%20others%20then%20ruled%20by%20the%20Congress%20(and%20now%20by%20the%20BJP)%20-%20such%20as%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20-%20also%20opposed%20the%20CAA%20and%20passed%20resolutions.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20Bengal%20and%20Kerala%20governments%20also%20stopped%20all%20NPR%2C%20or%20National%20Population%20Register%2C%20and%20NRC%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Telangana%2C%20the%20then-ruling%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20of%20ex-Chief%20Minister%20K%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%20also%20passed%20resolutions%20against%20all%20three%20and%20urged%20the%20government%20to%20%26quot%3Bremove%20all%20references%20to%20any%20religion%2C%20or%20to%20any%20foreign%20country%26quot%3B%20in%20view%20of%20fears%20expressed%20by%20lakhs%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20government%20-%20then%20also%20ruled%20by%20the%20Congress%20-%20also%20passed%20a%20resolution%2C%20and%2C%20significantly%2C%20several%20BJP%20leaders%20and%20lawmakers%20from%20the%20state%20also%20criticised%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20said%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20will%20help%20minorities%20from%20Muslim-dominated%20countries%20get%20citizenship%20if%20they%20fled%20due%20to%20religious%20persecution.%20However%2C%20critics%20say%20it%20is%20designed%20to%20discriminate%20against%20Muslims%20and%20violates%20secular%20principles%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710159900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-01%2F7j1sdvsg_delhi-crowded-market-reuters-pic_650x400_05_January_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com