20the%20appeal%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fi-feel-like-i-am-still-in-jail-acquitted-former-professor-gn-saibaba-5200217%5C%22%3Elong-imprisoned%20professor%20G.N.%20Saibaba%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20had%20been%20accused%20of%20participating%20in%20banned%20Maoist%20activities.%20Finding%20that%20such%20participation%20had%20not%20been%20established%20by%20the%20government%2C%20the%20justices%20ordered%20Professor%20Saibaba's%20release%2C%20which%20took%20place%20on%20March%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20subsequent%20interviews%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20Delhi%2C%20some%20of%20them%20accessible%20online%2C%20the%20Andhra-born%20professor%20has%20spoken%20of%20extreme%20physical%20and%20emotional%20hardships%20during%20his%20seven-year%20incarceration%2C%20which%2C%20among%20other%20things%2C%20resulted%20in%20his%20dismissal%20from%20Delhi%20University%2C%20where%20he%20taught%20for%20several%20years.%20In%20interviews%2C%20Saibaba%20has%20also%20spoken%20of%20the%20help%20he%20received%20from%20time%20to%20time%20from%20fellow%20prisoners%2C%20lawyers%2C%20and%20journalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20last%20point%20struck%20me%20as%20being%20extremely%20significant.%20When%20they%20discharge%20their%20professional%20or%20moral%20responsibilities%2C%20citizens%2C%20including%20prisoners%2C%20journalists%2C%20lawyers%20and%20those%20working%20in%20healthcare%2C%20also%20play%20a%20role%20in%20a%20democracy%2C%20whether%20or%20not%20anyone%20has%20heard%20their%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Unity%20Quotient%20Of%20INDIA%20Bloc%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20good%20reason%2C%20opposition%20parties%20as%20well%20as%20non-political%20citizens%20troubled%20by%20the%20state%20of%20India's%20democracy%20are%20agitated%20about%20who%20will%20get%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20next%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20form%20a%20new%20government.%20There%20are%20question%20marks%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F