%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20former%20education%20minister%20and%20senior%20DMK%20leader%20K%20Ponmudi%20in%20a%20disproportionate%20assets%20case.%20The%20court%20suspended%20the%20three-year%20prison%20sentence%20of%20his%20wife%2C%20leading%20to%20his%20immediate%20disqualification%20as%20an%20MLA.%20Earlier%2C%20in%20December%2C%20the%20Madras%20High%20Court%20sentenced%20him%20to%20three%20years%20of%20imprisonment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fsupreme-court-stays-conviction-of-dmk-leader-k-ponmudy-in-disproportionate-assets-case%2Farticleshow%2F108394194.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Top%20Court%20Setback%20For%20Bengal%2C%20Probe%20Against%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%20Stays%20With%20CBI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20setback%20to%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20dismissed%20its%20challenge%20to%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20order%20that%20transferred%20to%20the%20CBI%20investigation%20into%20an%20attack%20on%20a%20team%20of%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20officials%20in%20Bengal's%20Sandeshkhali.%20A%20team%20of%20ED%20officials%20had%20come%20under%20a%20mob%20attack%20on%20January%205%20when%20they%20went%20to%20the%20island%20to%20search%20properties%20linked%20to%20local%20strongman%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20of%20Justice%20BR%20Gavai%20and%20Justice%20Sandeep%20Mehta%20also%20questioned%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20government%20why%20it%20took%2050%20days%20to%20arrest%20Shahjahan.%20The%20now-expelled%20Trinamool%20leader%20is%20in%20the%20CBI's%20custody.%20Besides%20the%20case%20relating%20to%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20ED%20team%2C%20the%20strongman%20and%20his%20aides%20face%20allegations%20of%20land%20grab%2C%20extortion%20and%20sexual%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20had%20last%20week%20asked%20Bengal%20police%20to%20hand%20over%20Shahjahan's%20custody%20to%20the%20central%20agency.%20It%20had%20also%20come%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20state%20police.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20expunged%20the%20high%20court's%20observations%20on%20Bengal%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20query%20on%20why%20it%20took%2050%20days%20to%20arrest%20the%20strongman%2C%20Bengal%20police%20said%20a%20high%20court%20order%20had%20paused%20the%20investigation.%C2%A0%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20stay%20on%20investigation.%20We%20went%20back%20to%20court%2C%20asking%20for%20a%20clarification.%20It%20was%20clarified.%20Within%20one%20day%2C%20he%20was%20arrested%2C%26quot%3B%20senior%20advocate%20Jaideep%20Gupta%2C%20appearing%20for%20Bengal%20government%2C%20told%20the%20court.%C2%A0%26quot%3BTo%20say%20that%20the%20state%20police%20is%20delaying%20the%20investigation...these%20kinds%20of%20allegations%20are%20very%20damaging%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposing%20the%20Bengal%20government%2C%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20SV%20Raju%20referred%20to%20the%20January%205%20incident.%C2%A0%26quot%3BIn%20a%20case%20involving%20a%20ration%20scam%20running%20into%20crores%20of%20rupees%2C%20ED%20officials%20went%20to%20(the)%20house%20of%20this%20main%20accused.%20The%20door%20was%20not%20open%20and%20they%20were%20beaten%20up.%20They%20tried%20to%20water%20down%20the%20case%2C%20insofar%20as%20the%20assault%20of%20the%20ED%20officer%20is%20concerned.%20They%20filed%20some%20other%20case.%20That's%20why%20the%20investigation%20was%20stayed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0The%20Centre's%20counsel%20said%20Bengal%20police%20made%20%26quot%3Bno%20serious%20effort%26quot%3B%20to%20enter%20Shahjahan's%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20several%20cases%20of%20harassment%20against%20him.%20He%20has%20been%20patronised%20by%20local%20police%20and%20politicians.%20(For)%2057%20days%2C%20he%20is%20not%20available.%20Then%20overnight%20he%20appears%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Mr%20Raju%20also%20contested%20the%20state%20government's%20argument%20that%20a%20pause%20in%20the%20investigation%20stopped%20state%20police%20from%20arresting%20Shahjahan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Abhishek%20Singhvi%2C%20also%20appearing%20for%20Bengal%20government%2C%20flagged%20the%20high%20court's%20remarks%20on%20state%20police.%20When%20Mr%20Raju%20said%20these%20observations%20may%20be%20deleted%2C%20Mr%20Singhvi%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20those%20observations%20are%20deleted%2C%20then%20what%20are%20the%20grounds%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20observations%20against%20the%20police%20and%20the%20State%20government%20are%20deemed%20to%20be%20expunged%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20by%20residents%20of%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20an%20island%20in%20Bengal's%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district%2C%20have%20raised%20a%20political%20storm%20in%20the%20state.%20Shahjahan%2C%20who%20is%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20these%20allegations%2C%20was%20arrested%20last%20month%20after%20he%20was%20on%20the%20run%20for%2055%20days.%20What%20followed%20was%20a%20dramatic%20tug%20of%20war%20between%20central%20agencies%20and%20state%20police%20for%20the%20strongman's%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20one%20occasion%2C%20the%20state%20cops%20refused%20to%20hand%20him%20over%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20state%20government's%20challenge%20to%20the%20high%20court%20in%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20high%20court%2C%20however%2C%20held%20that%20its%20order%20had%20not%20been%20paused%20and%20directed%20Bengal%20police%20to%20hand%20over%20Shahjahan%20to%20CBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710153660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fe14mic4o_sheikh-shahjahan_625x300_29_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-sandeshkhali-case-sheikh-shahj