ation%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20of%20Hamil%20and%20others%20who%20had%20been%20sent%20before%20us%20to%20the%20Russian%20camps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20managed%20to%20establish%20contact%20with%20him%20on%20the%20phone%2C%20he%20told%20me%20that%20he%20was%20at%20another%20camp%20where%20foreigners%20like%20him%20are%20being%20trained%20to%20handle%20guns%2C%20grenades%20and%20dig%20trenches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamil%20could%20hear%20missiles%20and%20drones%20where%20he%20was%2C%20which%20means%20he%20was%20being%20trained%20very%20close%20to%20the%20frontline.%20He%20was%20petrified%20and%20broke%20down%20while%20speaking%20to%20me.%20After%2015%20days%E2%80%99%20training%2C%20he%20was%20to%20be%20deployed%20on%20the%20frontline.%20He%20said%20he%20may%20never%20get%20to%20see%20his%20family%20ever%20again%20as%20the%20reality%20of%20this%20bloody%20war%20hit%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20can%20any%20army%20raise%20a%20soldier%20with%20just%2015%20days%20of%20training%3F%20It%20takes%20years%20for%20a%20man%20to%20be%20trained%20for%20a%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20me%20to%20run%20away%20from%20the%20camp%20in%20Ryazan%20while%20I%20still%20had%20a%20chance.%20He%20told%20me%20to%20go%20back%20to%20India%20and%20tell%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20rescue%20him%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20a%20few%20weeks%2C%20Hamil%20died%20in%20a%20drone%20strike%20that%20landed%20on%20his%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20escape%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Moin%20started%20harassing%20us%20for%20money%20and%20asked%20us%20to%20send%20our%20ATM%20card%20details%20so%20he%20could%20withdraw%20our%20first%20salaries%20from%20our%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20received%20my%20salary.%20He%20started%20threatening%20to%20harm%20my%20family%20back%20home%20as%20he%20had%20my%20Aadhaar%20card%20details%20with%20my%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E