n%20the%20streets%20and%20sometimes%20resorted%20to%20picking%20food%20from%20dustbins%20to%20feed%20myself.%20At%20times%2C%20I%20went%20hungry%20for%204-5%20days.%20Whenever%20I%20spoke%20to%20my%20family%20on%20the%20phone%2C%20I%20lied%20to%20them%20about%20my%20well-being%20so%20that%20my%20parents%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20worry%20about%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20month%20of%20living%20like%20a%20beggar%2C%20I%20found%20Raja%20Pathan%20%E2%80%93%20a%20Youtuber%20who%20had%20joined%20the%20Russian%20Army%20last%20year%20and%20had%20managed%20to%20terminate%20his%20contract.%20He%20helped%20me%20with%20money%20to%20pay%20for%20a%20white%20passport%20at%20the%20embassy%20and%20booked%20my%20tickets%20for%20Delhi.%20Finally%2C%20I%20landed%20back%20in%20India%20on%20February%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERegret%20and%20remorse%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20was%20lucky%20to%20escape%20the%20horror%20but%20now%20I%20spend%20sleepless%20nights%2C%20haunted%20by%20the%20memories%20of%20Hamil%20and%20other%20men%20who%20were%20with%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20wonder%20how%20they%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamil%20wanted%20me%20to%20get%20back%20to%20India%20and%20try%20to%20rescue%20him%20with%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20help.%20But%20it%20was%20too%20late.%20He%20died%20before%20I%20could%20do%20anything%20to%20rescue%20him.%20The%20regret%20won%E2%80%99t%20let%20me%20be%20at%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20plead%20with%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20the%20scammers%20and%20rescue%20our%20men%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%20Time%20is%20running%20out.%20Every%20single%20day%20at%20the%20frontline%20is%20a%20call%20for%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAs%20told%20to%20Shalu%20Yadav.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710153019000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F11115218%2FFeatured-image.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frig