grocery%20shopping.%20She%20came%20with%20a%20mission%20to%20buy%20'curry%20spice'%20for%20my%20sister%20and%20couldn't%20believe%20there's%20more%20than%20one%20type.%20She%20took%20approximately%20a%20billion%20photos%20of%20weeds%20and%20plants%20in%20the%20most%20random%20places%20-%20she%20was%20a%20gardener%20before%20retiring%20and%20was%20at%20awe%20with%20the%20vegetation%20here%2C%20with%20what%20in%20Europe%20are%20an%20indoor%20plants%20requiring%20tonnes%20of%20maintenance%20just%20growing%20our%20in%20the%20wild%20next%20to%20some%20highway%20toilet%20stop%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kopec%20wrote%20while%20describing%20the%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20India%20is%20portrayed%20as%20a%20land%20with%20slums%20and%20overcrowded%20trains.%20However%2C%20a%20trip%20on%20the%20Vande%20Bharat%20Express%20Train%20changed%20the%20entire%20picture.%20%26quot%3BUnfortunately%20image%20of%20India%20in%20Poland%20is%20mostly%20portraying%20slums%20and%20overcrowded%20trains%20with%20people%20hanging%20on%20rooftops.%20Taking%20a%20perfectly%20on-time%20Vande%20Bharat%20debunked%20some%20stereotypes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EI've%20traveled%20with%20my%20mom%20in%20India%20%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3%20for%20a%20week%20and%20here's%20what%20she%20loved%20about%20it%20%E2%AC%87%EF%B8%8F%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIt%20was%20her%20first%20time%20out%20of%20Europe%20and%20she%20doesn't%20speak%20English.%20She's%20heard%20a%20lot%20about%20the%20country%20from%20me%2C%20read%20in%20Polish%20media%2C%20yet%20everything%20around%20here%20was%20shocking.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn1.%20The%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FY0Du0GSBwR%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FY0Du0GSBwR%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Szymon%20Kope%C4%87%20(%40szymonkopec)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fszymonkopec%2Fstatus%2F1766386263777784290%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%209%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20same%20goes%20for%20Dehli%20and%20its%20green%2C%20beautifully%20maintained%20neighbourhoods.%20%C2%A0Tech%20ecosystem%20blew%20her%20mind.%20In%20Poland%20we're%20so%20far%20behind%20in%20that%20regard%2C%20while%20here%20I've%20shown%20her%20that%20there's%20an%20app%20for%20literally%20anything%20she%20imagines%20%2B%206%20alternatives%20from%20competitors%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kopec%20added%20that%20they%20are%20not%20entirely%20taught%20about%20India's%20history.%20%26quot%3BVisiting%20Taj%20Mahal%20or%20forts%20in%20Jaipur%20was%20a%20eye-opening%20to%20what%20the%20country%20was%20for%20centuries%2C%20pre%20colonisation.%26quot%3B%20The%20executive%20concluded%20by%20saying%20that%20his%20mother%20was%20overjoyed%20by%20the%20hospitality%20and%20what%20%26quot%3Bshe%20loved%20the%20most%20were%20the%20people.%26quot%3B%20He%20shared%20a%20photo%20with%20his%20mother%20from%20the%20trip%20and%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThough%20she%20couldn't%20communicate%20with%20them%2C%20seeing%20joy%20all%20around%20and%20having%20these%20little%20interactions%20was%20precious%2C%20as%20everyone%20was%20beyond%20kind%20and%20we've%20had%200%20less-than-positive%20experiences.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Truecaller%20executive%20added%20that%20even%20though%20his%20mother%20is%20back%20home%2C%20%26quot%3Bshe%20hasn't%20stopped%20pitching%20India%20as%20an%20ideal%20holiday%20destination%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20family.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20being%20shared%2C%20the%20post%20has%20amassed%20over%208.5%20lakh%20views%20and%2021%2C000%20likes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20a%20wonderful%20read.%20Of%20course%20no%20place%20is%20perfect%20%26amp%3B%20we%20can%20always%20improve%20but%20I'm%20glad%20she%20had%20a%20delightful%20experience%20here.%20Next%20time%20she's%20here%20%26amp%3B%20if%20it's%20possible%20consider%20a%20trip%20to%20a%20hill%20station%20like%20Manali.%20The%20true%20beauty%20of%20both%20the%20country%20%26amp%3B%20the%20people%20in%20such%20places%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20user%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20person%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThat's%20very%20heartening%20to%20hear!%20Next%20trip%20please%20be%20our%20guests%20in%20Chandigarh%20%26amp%3B%20give%20us%20a%20chance%20to%20show%20you%20around%20parts%20of%20the%20Simla%20hills%20%26amp%3B%20green%20Punjab.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20person%20commented%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20so%20glad%20that%20you%20enjoyed%20the%20experience%20of%20India.It%20is%20indeed%20a%20wonderful%20place%20despite%20all%20the%20news%20and%20opinions%20floating%20around%20about%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThank%20you%20for%20sharing%20this.%20Like%20every%20country%2C%20India%20has%20its%20share%20of%20problems%2C%20which%20we%20need%20to%20work%20on%2C%20but%20it%20is%20so%20good%20to%20see%20people%20sharing%20their%20positive%20experiences%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20remarked%20a%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710152160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F0lgj3u28_truecaller-exec_625x300_11_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fvande-bharat-debunked-some-stereotypes-truecaller-executive-on-trip-to-india-5217788%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Truecaller%20executive%20added%20that%20even%20though%20his%20mother%20is%20back%20home%2C%20%26quot%3Bshe%20hasn't%20stopped%20pitching%20India%20as%20an%20ideal%20holiday%20destination%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20family.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fvande-bharat-debunked-some-stereotypes-truecaller-executive-on-trip-to-india-5217788%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fvande-bharat-debunked-some-stereotypes-truecaller-executive-on-trip-to-india-5217788%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fvande-bharat-debunked-some-stereotypes-truecaller-executive-on-trip-to-india-5217788%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Supreme%20Court%20Questions%20High%20Court's%20Shock%20Verdict%20On%20Child%20Pornography%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fsupreme-court%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%20red-flagged%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fmadras-high-court%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMadras%20High%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20decision%20to%20not%20consider%20the%20downloading%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fchild-pornography%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echild%20pornography%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20crime.%20A%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20issued%20notice%20to%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Police%20and%20the%20accused%20in%20this%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20hearing%20a%20plea%20challenging%20the%20High%20Court's%20shocking%20January%20ruling%20-%20that%20downloading%20child%20pornography%20is%20not%20an%20offence%20under%20POCSO%2C%20or%20Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20Act%2C%20or%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Act%20since%20such%20actions%20were%20taken%20%26quot%3Bin%20privacy%20without%20affecting%20or%20influencing%20anyone%20else%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20moment%20an%20accused%20tries%20to%20circulate%20or%20distribute%20or%20publicly%20exhibit%20obscene%20photos%20and%20videos%2C%20then%20the%20ingredients%20of%20the%20offence%20starts%20kicking%20in...%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20reasoned%20that%20to%20qualify%20as%20an%20offence%20under%20POCSO%2C%20and%20the%20IT%20Act%2C%20the%20accused%20had%20to%20have%20created%2C%20published%2C%20and%20transmitted%20the%20material.%20And%20wth%20relation%20to%20the%20IT%20Act%2C%20it%20said%20the%20relevant%20section%20did%20not%20cover%20cases%20where%20an%20individual%20only%20downloaded%20and%20watched%20content%2C%20without%20doing%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20therefore%20quashed%20proceedings%20against%20a%2028-year-old%20man%20who%20had%20been%20charged%20with%20downloading%20child%20pornographic%20content%20to%20his%20mobile%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadras-high-court-expresses-concern-over-gen-z-grappling-with-pornography-4850189%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMadras%20High%20Court's%20Concern%20Over%20Gen-Z%20%26quot%3BGrappling%26quot%3B%20With%20Porn%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20all%20legal%20action%20against%20the%20accused%20was%20dropped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20High%20Court%20did%2C%20however%2C%20complain%20about%20children%20today%20%26quot%3Bgrappling%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20issue%20of%20watching%20pornography%2C%20declaring%20it%20could%20have%20negative%20consequences%20years%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20declaring%20the%20accused%20to%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Bafflicted%20with%20this%20(watching%20pornography)%20addiction%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20court%20advised%20counselling%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bhealthy%20and%20happy%20future%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%20last%20year%2C%20the%20central%20government%20sent%20notices%20to%20social%20media%20platforms%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20YouTube%2C%20and%20Telegram%2C%20warning%20they%20would%20lose%20legal%20immunity%20unless%20they%20act%20on%20this%20issue%20urgently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20platforms%20were%20asked%20to%20permanently%20remove%2C%20or%20disable%20access%20to%2C%20child%20pornography%20content.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fact-on-child-pornography-or-lose-legal-immunity-centre-to-tech-giants-4457056%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BAct%20Against%20Child%20Porn%2C%20Or%20Lose%20Legal%20Immunity%26quot%3B%3A%20Centre%20To%20Tech%20Giants%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20centre's%20action%20followed%20reports%20that%20another%20social%20media%20platform%20-%20Instagram%20-%20is%20home%20to%20a%20vast%20network%20of%20such%20content%20being%20created%20and%20shared.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Finstagrams-algorithms-connect-vast-paedophile-network-seeking-child-pornography-report-4103916%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWall%20Street%20Journal%20report%20said%C2%A0Instagram's%20algorithms%20linked%20and%20promoted%20this%20network%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20people%20seeking%20illegal%20sexual%20content%20and%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710151620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fc1l320oo_supreme-court-ani_625x300_23_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-questions-madras-high-courts-shock-verdict-on-child-pornography-5217713%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Monday%20red-flagged%20a%20Madras%20High%20Court%20decision%20to%20not%20consider%20the%20downloading%20of%20child%20pornography%20as%20a%20crime.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-questions-madras-high-courts-shock-verdict-on-child-pornography-5217713%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampprojec