said%20this%20while%20issuing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20240309111128%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fpdf_upload%2Fcbdt-526938.pdf%5C%22%3Efresh%20and%20superseding%20guidelines%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20when%20senior%20officials%20can%20choose%20to%20expedite%20the%20disposal%20of%20income%20tax%20appeals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20new%20guidelines%2C%20there%20are%20five%20situations%20where%20appeals%20at%20a%20certain%20organisation%20level%20may%20be%20expeditiously%20disposed%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20when%20a%20case%20involves%20a%20demand%20higher%20than%20Rs%201%20crore%2C%20when%20VIPs%20or%20the%20PMO%20refers%20a%20case%2C%20when%20directions%20are%20received%20from%20a%20court%2C%20when%20senior%20citizens%20make%20requests%20or%20when%20a%20case%20involves%20genuine%20hardship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftaxguru.in%2Fincome-tax%2Fguidelines-priority-turn-disposal-appeals-csit-au-csit-appeals.html%5C%22%3EPrevious%20guidelines%20issued%20in%20December%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20mentioned%20five%20situations%20but%20VIP%20or%20PMO%20references%20were%20not%20one%20of%20them.%20Instead%2C%20they%20contained%20a%20provision%20for%20expeditious%20disposal%20where%20refunds%20were%20higher%20than%20Rs%201%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20guidelines%2C%20issued%20on%20Thursday%20(March%207)%2C%20deal%20with%20appeals%20pending%20at%20the%20Commissioner%20of%20Income%20Tax%20(Appeal%2FAppeal%20Unit)%20and%20Additional%20or%20Joint%20Commissioner%20of%20Income%20Tax%20(Appeal)%20organisational%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20say%20that%20requests%20for%20expeditious%20disposal%20that%20are%20either%20raised%20at%20the%20appellant%E2%80%99s%20instance%2C%20or%20are%20referred%20by%20an%20assessing%20officer%20or%20a%20range%20head%2C%20%E2%80%9Cmay%20be%20considered%E2%80%9D%20by%20Principal%20Commissioners%2C%20Chief%20Commissioners%20or%20Directors%20General%20of%20Income%20Tax%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20recommendations%20made%20by%20jurisdictional%20principal%20income%20tax%20commissioners%20among%20other%20ranks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20appeals%20within%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20faceless%20income%20tax%20appeals%20commissioners%20are%20concerned%2C%20the%20new%20guidelines%20say%20that%20requests%20for%20expeditious%20disposals%20shall%20be%20referred%20to%20a%20Principal%20Chief%20Commissioner%20of%20Income%20Tax%20(National%20Faceless%20Appeal%20Centre).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnarendra-modi-launches-new-transparent-taxation-platform-faceless%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98faceless%E2%80%99%20income%20tax%20assessment%20and%20appeals%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20created%20in%202020%20so%20that%20taxpayers%20would%20not%20have%20to%20physically%20visit%20income%20tax%20offices%20or%20meet%20officials%20in%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20intended%20to%20increase%20convenience%20for%20taxpayers%20and%20rein%20in%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710150640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F24135657%2Fcash-india.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpmo-vip-references-expeditious-income-tax-appeal-disposal-cbdt%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Central%20Board%20of%20Direct%20Taxes%20said%20this%20while%20issuing%20fresh%20and%20superseding%20guidelines%20last%20week%20on%20when%20senior%20officials%20can%20choose%20to%20expedite%20the%20disposal%20of%20income%20tax%20appeals.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpmo-vip-references-expeditious-income-tax-appeal-disposal-cbdt%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Top%20key%20quotes%20from%20PM%20Modi's%20speech%20in%20Gurgaon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710150187000%2C%22visual%