0Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20too%20has%20used%20this%20slogan%20in%20his%20speeches.%20However%2C%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20a%20senior%20leader%20has%20so%20openly%20explained%20why%20this%20number%20is%20important%20for%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHegde%E2%80%99s%20comments%20created%20an%20immediate%20controversy%2C%20with%20opposition%20leaders%20saying%20Hegde%20had%20revealed%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Chidden%20agenda%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHegde%E2%80%99s%20statement%20has%20exposed%20the%20ulterior%20motives%20of%20the%20BJP%20to%20replace%20Baba%20Saheb%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20version%20of%20the%20Constitution%20with%20their%20own%2C%20influenced%20by%20the%20Manusmriti.%20The%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20version%20would%20reinforce%20the%20evil%20practices%20of%20the%20caste%20system.%20The%20BJP%20will%20remove%20all%20reservations%20for%20OBCs%20and%20Dalits%20if%20they%20come%20to%20power.%20His%20statement%20is%20a%20direct%20attack%20on%20OBCs%20and%20Dalits%2C%E2%80%9D%20Karnataka%20chief%20minister%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Siddaramaiah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20Modi%20disagrees%20with%20Hegde%E2%80%99s%20opinions%2C%20he%20should%20first%20expel%20him%20from%20the%20party.%20Failing%20to%20act%20against%20Hegde%20suggests%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20implicit%20agreement.%20It%20seems%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20public%20declarations%20of%20allegiance%20to%20the%20Constitution%20are%20merely%20superficial%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAnant%20Kumar%20Hegde%E2%80%99s%20statement%20about%20the%20need%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20secure%20400%20seats%20to%20protect%20Hinduism%20by%20amending%20the%20Constitution%20is%20not%20his%20personal%20statement%20but%20a%20part%20of%20the%20secret%20agenda%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20Constitution%