%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Femergency-caribbean-summit-to-address-haiti-gang-crisis%2Famp_articleshow%2F108378782.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Femergency-caribbean-summit-to-address-haiti-gang-crisis%2Famp_articleshow%2F108378782.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre%20right%20wins%20Portugal%20election%20as%20far%20right%20surges%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710124060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F16D08%2Fproduction%2F_132884439_2509cdc9e3b53341ff4fc9d8db302b195d07e7da0_22_6000_33751000x563.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68526833%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Portugal%20heads%20for%20a%20minority%20government%20after%20a%20tight%20vote%20in%20which%20the%20far%20right%20makes%20big%20gains.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A189%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68526833%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68526833.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68526833.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Urban%20Employment%20Programmes%3A%20A%20Catalyst%20for%20Female%20Labour%20Force%20Participation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10173957%2Fbelle-maluf-MxF6x11ICWs-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20recent%20years%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20urban%20employment%20landscape%20has%20witnessed%20a%20new%20entrant%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Urban%20Employment%20Programmes%20(UEPs)%2C%20currently%20implemented%20across%20nine%20Indian%20states.%20The%20latest%20offering%20%E2%80%93%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Indira%20Gandhi%20Rozgar%20Yojna%20(IRGY)%20%E2%80%93%20was%20launched%20in%202022%20with%20an%20ambitious%20Rs%20800-crore%20budget%2C%20to%20address%20issues%20of%20urban%20poverty%2C%20inflation%20and%20joblessness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scale%20of%20these%20problems%20is%20large%2C%20and%20gendered.%20India%E2%80%99s%20unemployment%20rate%20remains%20around%208-9%25%2C%20yet%20the%20Periodic%20Labour%20Force%20Survey%20(PLFS)%20reveals%20that%20only%2021.9%25%20of%20women%20aged%2015%20and%20above%20in%20urban%20areas%20participate%20in%20the%20workforce%2C%20with%20a%20significant%2091%25%20employed%20in%20the%20informal%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20UEPs%20across%20India%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1003041%2Fhow-urban-employment-schemes-can-offer-social-security-to-the-poor-and-empower-women%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E%20note%20the%20predominance%20of%20women%20workers%2C%20and%20our%20research%20in%20Rajasthan%20suggests%20that%20over%2090%25%20of%20IRGY%20beneficiaries%20are%20women.%20These%20metrics%20indicate%20a%20positive%20movement%20towards%20gender%20inclusivity%20and%20empowerment.%20A%20review%20of%20UEPs%20across%20India%20and%20insights%20from%20the%20field%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20Odisha%20help%20us%20understand%20what%20draws%20women%20to%20these%20programmes%20and%20identify%20best%20practices%20and%20learnings%20that%20can%20lead%20to%20a%20sustained%20increase%20female%20labour%20force%20participation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20contexts%20and%20household%20dynamics%20are%20key%20determinants%20for%20lower%20female%20labour%20force%20participation.%20UEPs%20provides%20many%20women%20a%20pathway%20to%20enter%20the%20labour%20market%2C%20hitherto%20unavailable%20due%20to%20limited%20employment%20opportunities%2C%20unpaid%20care%20responsibilities%2C%20and%20other%20limitations%20placed%20by%20households%2C%20such%20as%20distance%20to%20work%2C%20work%20timings%2C%20and%20the%20concerns%20about%20safety%20outside%20the%20home%20and%20neighbourhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUEPs%20address%20these%20issues%20by%20offering%20a%20structured%20and%20supportive%20environment%20for%20women%20to%20enter%20the%20formal%20labour%20market.%20For%20informal%20workers%20such%20as%20home-based%20workers%2C%20UEPs%20substitute%20exploitative%20labour%20and%20wages%20(often%20as%20low%20as%20Rs.%2050%20a%20day)%20with%20a%20guaranteed%20minimum%20wage.%20Domestic%20workers%20benefit%20from%20a%20single%20worksite%2C%20reducing%20time%20and%20cost%20spent%20on%20commuting%2C%20and%20facilitating%20better%20management%20of%20household%20tasks.%20Similarly%2C%20casual%20workers%2C%20such%20as%20those%20in%20construction%2C%20find%20UEPs%20safer%20and%20easier%20to%20access%2C%20even%20if%20wages%20may%20be%20slightly%20lower.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22In%20Charts%3A%20How%20Women%20Continue%20to%20Shoulder%20the%20Burden%20of%20Unpaid%20Work%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fin-charts-how-women-continue-to-shoulder-the-burden-of-unpaid-work%5C%22%3EIn%20Charts%3A%20How%20Women%20Continue%20to%20Shoulder%20the%20Burden%20of%20Unpaid%20Work%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUEPs%20also%20offer%20a%20sense%20of%20safety%20for%20women%2C%20as%20many%20reported%20feeling%20safer%20due%20to%20the%20presence%20of%20other%20woman%20at%20the%20worksite.%20Women%20also%20found%20camaraderie%20and%20built%20stronger%20social%20networks%20at%20worksites.%20Ironically%2C%20these%20workspaces%20became%20unexpected%20spaces%20of%20leisure%20granting%20women%20a%20break%20from%20relentless%20household%20responsibilities.%20This%20support%20extended%20beyond%20the%20workday%2C%20with%20women%20forging%20friendships%20that%20helped%20navigate%20personal%20lives%20and%20crises.%20The%20programme%20also%20granted%20women%20a%20degree%20of%20autonomy%20by%20empowering%20them%20with%20financial%20resources%20and%20a%20role%20in%20household%20decision-making.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20not%20just%20social%20contexts%20that%20make%20UEPs%20attractive.%20Informal%20work%20is%20layered%20with%20precarities%2C%20one%20of%20which%20is%20the%20task%20of%20finding%20work%20frequently.%20UEPs%20guarantee%20work%20(up%20to%20125%20days%20in%20Rajasthan)%20and%20often%20back%20this%20promise%20with%20unemployment%20allowances.%20UEPs%20also%20offer%20multiple%20avenues%20for%20workers%20to%20register%20for%20work%2C%20including%20camps%20organised%20by%20Urban%20Local%20Bodies%20and%20Civil%20Society%20Organisations%2C%20online%20registration%2C%20and%20support%20centres%20like%20e-mitra.%20The%20diversity%20of%20options%20and%20quick%20enrolment%20significantly%20reduce%20the%20barriers%20to%20entry%20that%20women%20face%20when%20applying%20for%20other%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20despite%20these%20benefits%2C%20UEPs%2C%20face%20criticism%20for%20offering%20lower-than-market%20wages%2C%20and%20for%20excessive%20focus%20on%20manual%20labour%20and%20for%20the%20quality%20of%20employment.%20Considering%20these%20strengths%20and%20weaknesses%2C%20we%20recommend%20several%20improvements%20for%20UEPs%20to%20elevate%20female%20labour%20force%20participation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBroaden%20Eligibility%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Access%20to%20UEPs%20in%20India%20are%20mostly%20restricted%20to%20residents.%20Not%20only%20does%20this%20leave%20out%20migrant%20women%2C%20who%20are%20often%20more%20vulnerable%2C%20but%20also%20long-term%20residents%20who%20may%20be%20considered%20migrants%20%E2%80%98on%20paper%E2%80%99%20and%20unable%20to%20meet%20the%20eligibility%20criteria%2C%20enforced%20through%20requirements%20such%20as%20Aadhaar%2C%20ration%20cards%2C%20or%20voter%20ID%20cards.%20UEPs%20must%20consider%20non-local%20identification%2C%20such%20as%20Aadhaar%2C%20and%20ID%20cards%20generated%20through%20worker%20organisations%20or%20unions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOffer%20Flexible%20Work%20Options%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Recognising%20the%20burden%20of%20household%20work%2C%20UEPs%20can%20offer%20flexible%20work%20options%2C%20allowing%20women%20to%20choose%20shorter%20daily%20shifts%20of%20three%20to%20four%20hours%2C%20or%20condensed%20workweeks%20of%20two%20to%20three%20days.%20Similar%20employment%20programmes%20in%20South%20Africa%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.springer.com%2Fchapter%2F10.1057%2F9781137313997_4%5C%22%3EArgentina%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20offered%20such%20options.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.levyinstitute.org%2Fpubs%2Fwp_519.pdf%5C%22%3EArgentina%E2%80%99s%20Plan%20Jefes%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20effective%2C%20with%20nearly%2070%25%20of%20beneficiaries%20being%20women.%20Studies%20show%20improved%20access%20to%20social%20services%2C%20reduced%20school%20dropout%20rates%2C%20and%20lower%20levels%20of%20abuse%20and%20crime.%20Women%20also%20report%20gaining%20additional%20skills%2C%20improving%20their%20chances%20of%20obtaining%20other%20paid%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Despite%20Talk%20of%20Diversity%2C%20Women%20Still%20a%20Minority%20in%20Indian%20Boardrooms%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fdespite-talk-of-diversity-women-still-a-minority-in-indian-boardrooms%5C%22%3EDespite%20Talk%20of%20Diversity%2C%20Women%20Still%20a%20Minority%20in%20Indian%20Boardrooms%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExpand%20the%20Scope%20of%20Work%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20UEPs%20must%20target%20an%20expanded%20list%20of%20work%2C%20such%20as%20building%20and%20managing%20economic%20and%20social%20infrastructure%2C%20which%20can%20include%20childcare%20facilities%20(creches)%2C%20canteens%2C%20and%20multi-purpose%20centres%20(MPCCs)%20where%20women%20can%20collectivise%2C%20work%2C%20and%20rest.%20Women%20can%20also%20be%20granted%20work%20in%20community%20kitchens%2C%20and%20educational%20institutions%2C%20as%20well%20as%20public%20institutions%20such%20as%20Anganwaadis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImprove%20Accessibility%20and%20Mobility%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20UEPs%20should%20provide%20work%20closer%20to%20home%20and%20within%20a%201-2%20km%20radius%20to%20minimise%20transit%20time%20and%20cost.%20Alternatively%2C%20a%20transportation%20allowance%20(as%20practiced%20in%20Kerala)%20or%20free-to-use%20public%20transport%20can%20benefit%20women%20workers%20and%20enhance%20their%20mobility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrioritise%20Safety%20and%20Comfort%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Many%20women%20prefer%20UEPs%20because%20they%20provide%20safe%20spaces%20for%20decent%20work.%20Workplace%20amenities%20must%20include%20toilets%2C%20resting%20spaces%2C%20drinking%20water%2C%20and%20childcare%20facilities.%20This%20can%20set%20a%20positive%20benchmark%20for%20private%20markets%20as%20well%20and%20increase%20women%E2%80%99s%20labour%20force%20participation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWages%20and%20Skilling%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Typically%2C%20UEPs%20are%20aligned%20to%20minimum%20state%20wages.%20However%2C%20states%20must%20consider%20introducing%20the%20concept%20of%20living%20wages%2C%20which%20broadens%20the%20discussion%20on%20wages%20to%20include%20skill%20levels%2C%20and%20account%20for%20input%20factors%20such%20as%20the%20nature%20and%20location%20of%20work.%20A%20model%20such%20as%20this%20will%20additionally%20build%20a%20component%20of%20apprenticeship%2C%20allowing%20new%20and%20unskilled%20workers%20to%20learn%20from%20experienced%20workers%20and%20eventually%20find%20e%20permanent%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20UEPs%20are%20a%20vital%20lifeline%20for%20many%20women%20in%20urban%20India%2C%20high%20uptake%20should%20not%20be%20the%20end%20goal.%20UEPs%20must%20go%20beyond%20being%20safety%20nets%2C%20to%20imbibe%20not%20just%20protective%20and%20preventive%20measures%2C%20but%20transformative%20measures%20that%20address%20women%E2%80%99s%20labour%20force%20participation.%20This%20will%20need%20UEPs%20to%20adopt%20a%20more%20innovative%20approach%2C%20offering%20better%20wages%2C%20an%20expansive%20set%20of%20contextualised%20works%2C%20greater%20access%2C%20as%20well%20as%20safety%20and%20dignity.%20The%20true%20measure%20of%20success%20lies%20in%20building%20upon%20this%20foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVrashali%20Khandelwal%20is%20a%20Consultant%20at%20Indian%20Institute%20for%20Human%20Settlements%20(IIHS)%20and%20her%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Ework%20revolves%20around%20issues%20of%20informality%20and%20social%20protection.%20Sukrit%20Nagpal%20is%20a%20researcher%20and%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Epractitioner%20at%20IIHS%20and%20his%20work%20focuses%20on%20urban%20housing%20and%20informal%20work.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710122452000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10173957%2Fbelle-maluf-MxF6x11ICWs-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Furban-employment-programmes-a-catalyst-for-female-labour-force-participation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Urban%20employment%20programmes%20must%20go%20beyond%20being%20safety%20nets%2C%20to%20imbibe%20not%20just%20protective%20and%20preventive%20measures%2C%20but%20transformative%20measures%20that%20address%20women%E2%80%99s%20labour%20force%20participation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Furban-employment-programmes-a-catalyst-for-female-labour-force-participation%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22News%20agencies%20recall%20post-surgery%20image%20of%20UK's%20Princess%20Kate%20Middleton%20over%20manipulation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710121189000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108378156%2Cimgsize-1030815.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fnews-agencies-recall-post-surgery-image-of-uks-princess-kate-middleton-over-manipulation%2Farticleshow%2F108378