led%2C%20as%20was%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20entire%20training%20and%20education%20of%20the%20school.%20They%20did%20not%20necessarily%20have%20well-built%20bodies%20nor%20performed%20well%20in%20studies%2C%20drills%2C%20physical%20training%2C%20or%20shooting.%20Instead%2C%20some%20of%20them%20would%20not%20stand%20a%20chance%20in%20case%20they%20were%20even%20slapped.%20Most%20of%20them%20were%20lethargic%20rule%20breakers%20and%20often%20had%20to%20attend%20the%20punishment%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20did%20not%20have%20the%20moral%20high%20ground%2C%20yet%20they%20were%20powerful.%20They%20were%20loud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20always%20present%2C%20generating%20clamour.%20Despite%20their%20obnoxious%20demeanour%2C%20they%20always%20found%20ways%20to%20get%20away%2C%20seized%20the%20best%20opportunities.%20Cadets%20like%20me%20felt%20like%20losers.%20We%20followed%20rules%2C%20never%20bunked%20classes%2C%20or%20missed%20the%20devastating%20morning%20PT%20or%203%20am%20drill.%20But%20there%20were%20no%20prizes%20for%20us.%20Whereas%20our%20bullies%20always%20received%20rewards.%20We%20thought%20they%20would%20always%20win.%20We%20were%20hopeless%20and%20tempted%20to%20give%20up.%20We%20would%20simply%20succumb%20to%20their%20bullying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFar%E2%80%93right%20parties%2C%20much%20like%20those%20bullies%2C%20are%20loud.%20They%20yell%2C%20they%20shout%2C%20they%20bulldoze%2C%20the%20vocal%20minority%20claps%20in%20approval%2C%20and%20they%20win.%20And%20non-far-right%20parties%20and%20individuals%20often%20perceive%20them%20as%20unbeatable%2C%20thinking%20that%20bullies%20have%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-far-right-is-not-the-people%5C%22%3Epeople%E2%80%99s%20support.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20psychology%20is%20demoralised%2C%20defeated.%20This%20is%20not%20to%20claim%20moral%20or%20intellectual%20superiority%2C%20nor%20do%20we%20seek%20to%20dismiss%20far%E2%80%93right%20as%20street%20goons.%20That%20would%20be%20a%20self-defeating%20trope.%20But%20the%20goodness%20in%20us%20makes%20us%20play%20it%20safe%2C%20becoming%20cautious%20citizens%2C%20effectively%20rendering%20us%20inactive%20and%20hesitant%20to%20take%20initiatives%20that%20might%20involve%20even%20the%20slightest%20possibility%20of%20risk.%20We%20avoid%20trouble%2C%20shy%20away%20from%20confrontation.%20And%20should%20we%2C%20really%3F%20It%20drains%20us%2C%20it%20is%20an%20exhausting%20and%20persistent%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20liberal%20political%20commentators%20have%20been%20quick%20to%20attribute%20extremist%20acts%20of%20religious%20vandalism%20to%20fringe%20elements.%20They%20dismissed%20them%20as%20outside%20the%20mainstream%20political%20discourse.%20However%2C%20over%20the%20past%20decade%20under%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20rule%2C%20we%20have%20witnessed%20the%20transformation%20of%20once-termed%20%E2%80%9Cfringe%E2%80%9D%20tactics%20into%20tools%20employed%20by%20democratically%20elected%20governments.%20JCBs%20and%20bulldozers%20have%20evolved%20into%20symbols%20of%20instant%20justice.%20Persecution%20through%20non-judicial%20state%20apparatus%20has%20become%20a%20primary%20method.%20Every%20other%20political%20discourse%2C%20particularly%20in%20North%20and%20Northeast%20India%2C%20reinforces%20the%20view%20that%20these%20fringes%20are%20no%20longer%20on%20the%20outskirts%20but%20have%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20become%20part%20of%20the%20mainstream.%20And%20they%20truly%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20are%20they%20also%20the%20majority%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20ways%20to%20respond%20to%20it.%20One%2C%20who%20has%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-received-almost-90-of-all-corporate-donations-to-political-parties-in-2022-23%23%3A~%3Atext%3DADR%2527s%2520report%2520also%2520highlighted%2520the%2Cwent%2520to%2520the%2520BJP%2520alone.%5C%22%3Eresources%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20Two%2C%20what%20is%20playing%20on%20the%20screens%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20times%20of%20digital%20transformation%2C%20misinformation%20and%20troops%20of%20favourable%20video%20editors%20can%20sway%20voters%20and%20construct%20imagery%20of%20leaders%20and%20parties%20far%20removed%20from%20truth.%20For%20example%2C%20consider%20the%20case%20of%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20the%20two%20primary%20political%20rivals%20who%20happen%20to%20be%20approximately%20in%20the%20same%20age%20group.%20Trump%2C%20at%2077%2C%20and%20Biden%2C%20at%2081%2C%20are%20merely%20four%20years%20apart%20in%20age.%20Yet%20a%20campaign%20spotlighting%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20age%20in%20the%20United%20States%20gains%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2F2023%2F08%2F29%2Fbiden-trump-2024-age-legal-issues%5C%22%3Etraction%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20a%20similar%20focus%20on%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClearly%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fpolitics-news%2Ftrump-vs-biden-two-70-somethings-go-it-over-age-n998926%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CSleepy%20Joe%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20propaganda%20caught%20up%20on%20TikTok%20and%20within%20mainstream%20media%2C%20siding%20with%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20narrative.%20This%20pattern%20parallels%20the%20propaganda%20in%20India%20where%20the%20BJP%20labels%20the%20opposition%20as%3Cem%3E%20%E2%80%98pappu%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20(incompetent)%20and%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fvideo%2Faisa-mauka-phir-kaha-milega-pm-modi-mocks-congress-chief-in-rajya-sabha-2498752-2024-02-07%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAdvertisement-%2C%2527Aisa%2520mauka%2520phir%2520kaha%2520milega%2527%253A%2520PM%2520Modi%2520mocks%2CCongress%2520chief%2520in%2520Rajya%2520Sabha%26amp%3Btext%3DPrime%2520Minister%2520Narendra%2520Modi%2520on%2CPresident%2527s%2520Address%2520in%2520Rajya%2520Sabha.%5C%22%3Echaracterisation%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%E2%80%99s%20parliamentary%20speech%20as%20%E2%80%9Centertaining%E2%80%9D%20is%20followed%20by%20a%20campaign%20on%20prime-time%20TV%2C%20shaping%20the%20debate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Fmedia%2Frepublic-debates-study-shows-channel-promotoes-modi-ndtv%5C%22%3Eagenda%20set%20by%20the%20far%E2%80%93right%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDigital%20competition%20is%20brutal%2C%20unkind%20and%20leaves%20no%20space%20for%20truth%20to%20travel%20faster%20than%20an%20entertaining%20lie.%20If%20anything%2C%20digital%20outlook%20thrives%20on%20it.%20Social%20media%20platforms%20and%20online%20spaces%20provide%20a%20megaphone%20for%20extreme%20views%2C%20amplifying%20their%20impact%20beyond%20their%20numerical%20presence.%20The%20far-right%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20command%20attention%20is%20confused%20with%20broad%20public%20endorsement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20those%20of%20us%20in%20our%20school%2C%20which%20was%20equally%20diverse%20like%20the%20Indian%20demographics%2C%20the%20majority%20electorate%20is%20silent.%20Only%20a%20handful%20of%20individuals%2C%20often%20the%20same%20set%20of%20familiar%20faces%2C%20appear%20to%20be%20vocal%2C%20ringing%20the%20bell%20and%20warning%20us%20about%20the%20challenges%20facing%20our%20democracy.%20The%20silent%20majority%20watches%20far-right%20propaganda%20capturing%20discourse%20but%20sits%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Fwhat-explains-the-political-rights-ascendancy-to-global-power%5C%22%3EWhat%20Explains%20the%20Political%20Right%E2%80%99s%20Ascendancy%20to%20Global%20Power%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENon-far-right%20parties%20misread%20this%20and%20take%20a%20cautious%20approach.%20If%20recent%20election%20results%20(Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20and%20Telangana)%20tell%20us%20anything%2C%20it%20is%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20people%E2%80%9D%20want%20the%20far-right%20BJP%20to%20be%20reined%20in.%20Non-far-right%20parties%20often%20take%20cues%20from%20the%20electoral%20success%20of%20the%20far-right%20and%20overestimate%20people%E2%80%99s%20affinity%20to%20traditional%20values%20or%20a%20sense%20of%20narrow%20nationalism.%20In%20the%20process%2C%20they%20lose%20sight%20of%20the%20silent%20majority%2C%20which%20cares%20about%20democratic%20values%20like%20equality%20and%20wants%20a%20government%20that%20delivers%20on%20public%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20elections%20reveal%20that%20co-opting%20far-right%20issues%2C%20such%20as%20soft%20Hindutva%20%E2%80%93%20projecting%20the%20%E2%80%98Ram%20Van%20Gaman%20Marg%E2%80%99%20as%20an%20achievement%20of%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20government%20%E2%80%93%20did%20not%20help%20them%20win%20votes.%20If%20anything%2C%20it%20cast%20doubt%20among%20voters%20about%20the%20political%20ideology%20of%20the%20non-far-right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leaders%20like%20Kamal%20Nath%20focused%20on%20the%20clamorous%20voices%20of%20the%20far-right%2C%20and%20risked%20neglecting%20more%20tempered%20and%20nuanced%20views%2C%20resulting%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FVigneshJourno%2Fstatus%2F1732426232841506924%2Fphoto%2F1%5C%22%3Elosses%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fbjp-3-1-assembly-election-results-in-madhya-pradesh-rajasthan-chhattisgarh-telangana-congress-2024-challenges%2Farticle67601613.ece%5C%22%3Eurban%20and%20semi-rural%20areas%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Whereas%2C%20in%20Telangana%2C%20the%20Congress%20presented%20an%20alternative%20ideological%20agenda%20and%20did%20not%20play%20on%20the%20far-right%E2%80%99s%20turf.%20Evidence%20from%20these%204-state%20elections%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-wave-welfare-schemes-modi-popularity-women-voters-2023-assembly-election-results-analysis%2Farticle67618017.ece%5C%22%3Esuggests%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Congress%20vote%20share%20increased%20in%2