%5C%22wp-image-343999%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221186%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENidhi%20and%20Rajni%20started%20making%20the%20hair%20oil%20for%20their%20own%20use%20in%202020%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20they%20had%20given%20their%20oil%20to%20over%20200%20people%20in%20the%20society%2C%20the%20software%20engineer%20realised%20the%20viability%20of%20her%20business.%20As%20orders%20increased%2C%20they%20bought%20bigger%20vessels%2C%20a%20five%20litre%20and%2010%20litre%20kadhai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202023%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20increase%20their%20presence%20and%20set%20up%20an%20Instagram%20account%2C%20%E2%80%98Nidhi%E2%80%99s%20Grandmaa%20Secret%E2%80%99.%20Nidhi%E2%80%99s%20husband%2C%20Rajat%2C%20is%20a%20digital%20marketeer%20and%20helped%20her%20with%20her%20social%20media%20presence.%20One%20of%20their%20reels%20went%20viral%2C%20and%20led%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20orders.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20they%20had%20100%20orders%20on%20their%20hands!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNidhi%20was%20overwhelmed%20and%20wondered%20how%20we%20would%20fulfil%20so%20many%20orders.%20I%20reassured%20her%20that%20we%20would%20be%20able%20to%20do%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Rajni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challenge%20Nidhi%20faced%20initially%20was%20mental%2C%20as%20she%20wondered%20if%20they%20could%20succeed%2C%20and%20build%20a%20business%20from%20home.%20Having%20worked%20in%20a%20corporate%20environment%2C%20she%20worried%20about%20the%20intricacies%20involved%20in%20setting%20up%20a%20business%20from%20scratch%2C%20especially%20one%20that%20is%20very%20laborious%20and%20customer-centric.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20worried%20if%20this%20hair%20oil%20would%20work%20on%20everyone.%20My%20idea%20was%20to%20help%20people%20manage%20hair%20fall.%20I%20never%20thought%20of%20doing%20a%20business%20and%20was%20unsure%20of%20facing%20everyting%20that%20it%20involved%2C%E2%80%9D